        <item>
            <title>Google 推出自己的「推理」AI 模型 Gemini 2.0 Flash Thinking</title>
            <description>&lt;figure class=&quot;caas-figure&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-figure-with-pb&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-img-container&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;caas-img has-preview&quot; alt=&quot;Gemini 2.0&quot; src=&quot;https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-12/33aa2c20-be7b-11ef-bbf7-adb9a5dc3cb9&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caption-wrapper caption-aligned-with-image&quot;&gt;&lt;figcaption class=&quot;caption-collapse&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Gemini 2&lt;/span&gt;.0&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;虽然这两个礼拜是 OpenAI 的「12 天发表活动」，但感觉 Google 在一旁的发表是只多不少。继 &lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:1;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://hk.news.yahoo.com/gemini-20-is-googles-most-capable-ai-model-yet-and-available-to-preview-today-184836137.html&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:Gemini 2.0;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;&quot; class=&quot;link  yahoo-link&quot;&gt;Gemini 2.0&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:2;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://hk.news.yahoo.com/jarvis-googles-web-browsing-ai-is-now-officially-known-as-project-mariner-020002114.html&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:Project Mariner;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;&quot; class=&quot;link  yahoo-link&quot;&gt;Project Mariner&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:3;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://hk.news.yahoo.com/googles-gemini-deep-research-tool-is-here-to-answer-your-most-complicated-questions-050018540.html&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:Deep Research;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;&quot; class=&quot;link  yahoo-link&quot;&gt;Deep Research&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:4;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://hk.news.yahoo.com/googles-new-ai-video-model-sucks-less-at-physics-040026000.html&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:Veo 2;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;&quot; class=&quot;link  yahoo-link&quot;&gt;Veo 2&lt;/a&gt; 等新产品之后，Google 还在稍早推出了自己的「推理」模型 Gemini 2.0 Flash Thinking。它除了能回答复杂的问题外，还能提供其「思考」的过程，和 OpenAI 的 o1 有些类似。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;在 &lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:5;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://x.com/JeffDean/status/1869790032296579169&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:X 上的一篇贴文;cpos:5;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;X 上的一篇贴文&lt;/a&gt;中，Google DeepMind 首席科学家 Jeff Dean 表示，该模型「可以透过思考来加强其推理能力」，并且还受益于更快的 Gemini Flash 2.0 模型带来的速度。Dean 分享的示范展示了 Gemini 2.0 Flash Thinking 如何透过在提供解决方案之前「思考」一系列步骤来回答一个物理问题。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;twitter-tweet-wrapper&quot; data-embed-anchor=&quot;330a3678-8ac7-58c4-aebe-8fc305137544&quot;&gt;&lt;blockquote placeholder=&quot;&quot; data-theme=&quot;light&quot; class=&quot;twitter-tweet&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-card-loader small fixed-height&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Want to see Gemini 2.0 Flash Thinking in action? Check out this demo where the model solves a physics problem and explains its reasoning. &lt;a href=&quot;https://t.co/Nl0hYj7ZFS&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:pic.twitter.com/Nl0hYj7ZFS;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;pic.twitter.com/Nl0hYj7ZFS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;— Jeff Dean (@JeffDean) &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/JeffDean/status/1869790032296579169?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:December 19, 2024;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;December 19, 2024&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;严格来说这，这和人类进行的「推理」还是有点差异。它</description>
            <link>https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B3%87%E5%AE%89%E8%82%A1%E6%96%B0%E5%85%B5%E5%A0%B1%E5%88%B0-%E5%89%B5%E6%B3%93%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E8%A8%82%E5%96%AE%E8%83%BD%E8%A6%8B%E5%BA%A6%E9%AB%98-%E8%99%95%E9%9B%99%E4%BD%8D%E6%95%B8%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7-014753122.html</link>
